{
  "stem": "22047.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Following that, I, I was assigned to a, a program called Viking, which was a Mars lander.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we launched that and orbited Mars and set the lander down on the surface of Mars to look for life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we didn't find any.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now, more recently, there was a big hoopla by NASA, National Aeronautics and Space Administration, that they have found a rock in the Antarctic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they're analyzing that rock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And, and they think that if they find life in that rock, that there's life on Mars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't find any with Viking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Of course, we were in one spot with the lander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we dug up the Martian soil and didn't find any, any life in that episode.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But there is a big plan, as I understand, to send unmanned rovers to Mars and rove around the surface and take samples and see if, indeed, there could have been-- could've been life on Mars some eons ago.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Following that, I worked on a-- on a program called Voyager, which was a fly-by of Saturn and Jupiter and Uranus, Uranus and Neptune.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that was in 1977.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And those two spacecraft are way out beyond the solar system by now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And after that program, I left the employ of JPL and went to-- because I had met Marge in 1960.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She had-- she was my secretary at the time at Aerojet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And in 1977, we were married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I was working at JPL.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And she had moved a company that she had been founder of in Orange County, moved it to Monterey.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And so here's, here's my-- well, it's actually before we were married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "She moved the company up here in 1973.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
